    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0124-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:24:00.921+09:00">“Those who get the idea have nothing to say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:24:12.143+09:00">and neither do those who know everything. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:24:21.867+09:00">Speaking by saying nothing is still speech;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:24:32.352+09:00">taking knowing nothing to be knowledge is still knowing. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:24:44.444+09:00">Saying nothing and not speaking,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:24:59.019+09:00">knowing nothing and not knowing—</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:25:11.232+09:00">these are still speech, still knowledge. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:25:25.953+09:00">And there is nothing unsaid,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:25:38.367+09:00">nothing unknown,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:25:48.662+09:00">yet nothing said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:25:59.203+09:00">nothing known. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:26:07.422+09:00">That’s simply the way it is—</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T11:26:36.936+09:00">why are you randomly surprised?”</seg>
                </p>
